gry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔理佢收左錢定自己支持，<br />\n啲廢老都就兩腳一伸，仲要禍害香港，<br />\n搞完拍拍手就走左去，當日支持佢地班廢中，<br />\n依家自己受返，就屈年輕人搞亂香港，依家當權嘅先係罪魁禍首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"384dfeacc37b83ac35bcf019e03d4dd2c27634f1","tid":785096,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c19108021598e92e82d1c68cf1d92db15df50b39","tid":785096,"uid":115959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T02:38:32.000Z","msg":"唔舒服洗唔洗交醫生紙俾管理處？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T02:44:23.000Z","msg":"做乜唔早一個禮拜申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca17a5f0bb364becf8e5fcb171892ffd05331c2","tid":785096,"uid":27261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T02:57:25.000Z","msg":"其實要睇番份租約點寫<br />\n有d講到明要一個星期營業幾多日，幾多個鐘。<br />\n如果一早知果日要放假的，早少少貼張紙在閘位通知下多數都ok<br />\n係依間管理公司做野咁撚死板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有d野隻眼開隻眼閉咪算，無野找野黎做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：物管狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1383c8dfc634f9ce7bbd11dba3eec2efa25a2e48","tid":785096,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T05:01:11.000Z","msg":"又係領匯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次最衰搞埋外判<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"547717a11eba2f498960770e40897fda2bc67ea3","tid":785096,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0135913561881b1797e6a21071e45735b02c396a","tid":785096,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"